		<defName>TSOA_AnimaGrassResource</defName>
		<label>anima grass</label>
		<description>A bundle of anima grass. Harvested properly, the grass somehow remains alive, faintly humming with psychic resonance. It can be used in specialized crafting or ritual work.</description>
