	</ThingDef>
	
	<ThingDef ParentName="ResourceBase">
		<defName>TSOA_AnimaAmber</defName>
		<label>anima amber</label>
		<description>Crystalized anima sap, distilled and purified into a gemstone that glows with inner power. Merely being in its presence is uncomfortable, as it thrums with a resonance that is felt like a pressure on the mind. Its immense power can fuel the mightiest of crafts and rituals.</description>
